org.sysfoundry.kiln.base.sys

Interface SysBuilder

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseSysBuilder

    public interface SysBuilder
    The SysBuilder is an abstraction of a System builder in kiln. SysBuilder instances can compose and build a system as specified by the developer of the system.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      Sys build()
      The build method is expected to consider all the specifications used during the Sys building process and then return a fully constructed Sys instance.

    • Method Detail

      • build

        Sys build()
        The build method is expected to consider all the specifications used during the Sys building process and then return a fully constructed Sys instance. The Sys instance allows the boot strap script to start he instance of Sys
        Returns:
        The Sys which is used to start the system
